<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个怪物有着猪的鼻子和耳朵，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他像人一样，用两只脚走路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又挥舞起了钉耙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用他的金箍棒挡住了钉耙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐当！悟空用金箍棒去砸那只猪的脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”那只猪叫了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他脸向下倒在了土里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又跳了起来：“你一定会后悔的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那猪用钉耙砸了过来，悟空跳到了一边，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>结果钉耙砸在了一块巨石上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>双方打斗了起来，打得尘土飞扬，石头满地滚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧躲在自己的马后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“投降吧！”悟空又挥起金箍棒，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是孙悟空。五百年前，我大闹天宫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>打败了玉帝的所有天兵天将！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说过你。”那只猪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在我看来，你没那么厉害！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又朝着悟空冲去。悟空跳到了一边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以为你还在受罚。”那只猪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又举起了钉耙：“你不是被困在山下了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在自由了。”悟空说，“我要陪唐僧去往西天......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧！”那只猪大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他扔了钉耙。“我也要和他一起去的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我受罚被贬到了人间。”那只猪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是猪八戒。我也在天庭惹了麻烦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音说，如果我保护唐僧西天取经，我可以被宽恕。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摸了摸下巴。“好！”他说，“你拿行李。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猪八戒加入了队伍，三个人继续往西走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一路走着，那只猪一直抱怨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些行李太重了！我们要一直带着吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要再抱怨了！”悟空厉声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去西天极乐世界本来就是很辛苦的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猪八戒嘟囔着说：“我饿了。我们什么时候才能吃午饭？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧皱起了眉：“我们刚吃了早饭。你怎么又饿了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们绕了一个弯，看到了一只大老虎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟空迅速拿出了他们的兵器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”八戒高叫，“你在这里干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的主人，伟大的黄风怪正在举行宴会。”老虎说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着唐僧：“我们正在找可以吃的人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧的脸变得苍白，从马上摔了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你胆敢伤害我们的师父！”八戒警告说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是唐僧。他要去西天取经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老虎睁大了眼睛：“我听说过，吃了唐僧肉可以长生不老。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老虎亮出了他的爪子，然后朝着八戒冲过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒用钉耙打到了老虎。老虎摔倒在地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空举着金箍棒朝着老虎冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老虎躲过了悟空的金箍棒，又差点被钉耙打中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转身逃走了。悟空和八戒追赶着老虎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，老虎不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在一些灌木后面发现了一道黄色的光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在那里！”八戒低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和八戒悄悄地接近了灌木丛，但老虎不在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>岩石上铺了张老虎皮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了：“他太害怕了，连皮都脱了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拍了拍八戒的背：“我们真的是很厉害的护卫！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这两个朋友回到路上，一路笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他们的笑声停止了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！不！”悟空大叫，“师父去哪儿了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>